description: Newer Construction Designer Penthouse w/ Ocean views. Turnkey City Point penthouse decorated by one of Boston's leading interior designers and being sold fully furnished (or empty). Direct elevator access opens to a sprawling kitchen, dining & living area w/ stunning water views. Living area features stone fireplace, custom walnut cabinets, dry bar & plenty of sunlight. Private deck looks directly at Ocean and is perfect for entertaining. Dining area w/ custom chandelier & dining table. Ktichen w/ European cabinets, Wolf & Sub Zero appliances & Calcutta gold quartz countertops. Huge primary bedroom has custom walk-in closet, en-suite marble bath with double vanity & radiant floors. Spacious 2nd & 3rd bedroom each have custom closets. Custom window treatments, motorized shades, laundry & central AC. 2 garage parking (side by side). East Side location with easy walk to beaches, yacht clubs, restaurants & more. This penthouse has been beautifully designed & decorated and is move-in ready.
